      <title>欧洲央行的Stournaras说，美国对四月降低的障碍没有关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/ecb-s-stournaras-says-us-tariffs-no-obstacle-to-april-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计美国政府宣布的关税将“对欧元区的GDP增长率产生负面影响，首先是第一年的0.3％至0.4％的订单，欧洲中央银行管理理事会成员Yannis Sournaras告诉Bloomberg News。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/ecb-s-stournaras-says-us-tariffs-no-obstacle-to-april-rate-cut</guid>
