    <item>
      <title>纳格尔说，美国关税将使欧洲央行的政策进度进行测试</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/nagel-says-us-tariffs-will-put-ecb-policy-progress-to-the-test</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据理事会议员约阿希姆·纳格尔（Joachim Nagel）称，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的一系列关税威胁着全球经济，并质疑欧洲中央银行在与通货膨胀作斗争中取得的成就。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/nagel-says-us-tariffs-will-put-ecb-policy-progress-to-the-test</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 06:47:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普关税威胁经济增长时，欧洲的股票下沉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/european-stock-futures-decline-as-trump-tariffs-hurt-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）宣布了一个世纪以来对其贸易伙伴的最陡峭的美国关税之后，欧洲股票下跌，其中包括誓言报复的欧盟20％的税率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/european-stock-futures-decline-as-trump-tariffs-hurt-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:57:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球股票下沉，随着贸易商的削减风险：市场包裹的债券，债券上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）竞标重制世界贸易秩序之后，全球金融市场遭到了彻底的抛售，这比预期的要比预期的要积极进取。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:34:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普的关税增加了全球增长的风险时，害怕抓住市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/fear-grips-markets-as-trump-tariffs-raise-risks-to-global-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[短暂的一刻，华尔街对唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税计划的最严重的恐惧被放错了地方。救济集会开始在市场上荡漾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/fear-grips-markets-as-trump-tariffs-raise-risks-to-global-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:43:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼克基（Nikkei）225次低迷至8月以来特朗普的24％关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/japan-s-stock-futures-fall-as-trump-unveils-tariffs-yen-rises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本的蓝芯片尼克（Nikkei）225股票的平均水平下降到自八月以来的最低水平，此前唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统根据一项计划对全球贸易伙伴的税收征收24％的出口税率。日元更强的日元也对出口商股票进行了权衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/japan-s-stock-futures-fall-as-trump-unveils-tariffs-yen-rises</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:26:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国不包括钢，铝，黄金来自相互关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/us-excludes-steel-aluminum-copper-gold-from-reciprocal-tariff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫周三表示，钢铁，铝和一长串其他金属不会受到“互惠”关税的限制，此举为国内买家提供了救济，并建议政府对美国非常依赖进口商品的商品行事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/us-excludes-steel-aluminum-copper-gold-from-reciprocal-tariff</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 21:43:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
